Clone WordPress website all files/folders including database to a new folder on the same server and fix the permissions as well.

#What needs to be configured first
root_directory -- Points to the server root path, not including the current wordpress installation
wp_directory -- The folder name of the current wordpress installation that you want to clone
wp_clone_directory_name -- The folder name of the clone version, assumed to be under the roor directory

#Keep in mind
This script has not been fully tested, and I do not bring any responsibility for any harm that it may caused.
